      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and the interior is clean and free of major wear or tears. While the exterior is generally attractive, you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. It represents a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality car that has many miles left to give.",
